Your brain is... fresh.

604
00:35:11,900 --> 00:35:13,600
Maybe he is a little old-fashioned.

605
00:35:13,601 --> 00:35:14,601
But look at him.

606
00:35:15,150 --> 00:35:16,600
He's so in tune with his element.

607
00:35:16,601 --> 00:35:19,600
He can travel across the entire ocean.

608
00:35:19,601 --> 00:35:20,600
With no map.

609
00:35:20,601 --> 00:35:21,600
No instruments.

610
00:35:21,601 --> 00:35:26,600
There's so much I can learn from him.

611
00:35:33,600 --> 00:35:41,600
I'd give anything to be able
to see my air bison again.

612
00:35:41,601 --> 00:35:48,600
And now... To see
only one remains.

613
00:35:53,250 --> 00:35:54,650
You said our people were wiped out.

614
00:35:55,750 --> 00:35:56,600
Yet you survived.

615
00:35:56,601 --> 00:35:57,600
How?

616
00:35:57,601 --> 00:36:02,600
I had just found out I was the Avatar.

617
00:36:02,601 --> 00:36:05,601
But... The responsibility...

618
00:36:06,800 --> 00:36:07,800
It was too much.

619
00:36:09,450 --> 00:36:10,600
So I ran away.

620
00:36:10,601 --> 00:36:14,600
While I was gone... The
Fire Nation attacked.

621
00:36:16,600 --> 00:36:18,600
They were looking for me.

622
00:36:21,600 --> 00:36:25,600
If... If I'd just been
there... Sonam would say...

623
00:36:27,000 --> 00:36:28,600
Air Nomads are formed from the mist.

624
00:36:30,250 --> 00:36:31,810
We walk the world for a moment in time.

625
00:36:33,150 --> 00:36:35,600
Then we return to the eternal wind.

626
00:36:35,601 --> 00:36:38,600
Monkiazzo taught me that.

627
00:36:38,650 --> 00:36:41,600
We carry the same weight.

628
00:36:41,601 --> 00:36:44,600
A grief no one else could
possibly comprehend.

629
00:36:46,000 --> 00:36:47,600
But you and I can heal the past.

630
00:36:47,800 --> 00:36:51,600
Let me show you how
powerful our element can be.

631
00:36:51,850 --> 00:36:53,600
When airbenders work together.

632
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:59,600
What are you doing?

633
00:36:59,601 --> 00:37:01,600
This is how Sonam taught me.

634
00:37:01,601 --> 00:37:04,600
Feel the energy that tethers us.

635
00:37:08,600 --> 00:37:11,600
The bond between us.

636
00:37:11,601 --> 00:37:13,600
Can you feel it?

637
00:37:13,601 --> 00:37:14,600
Use it!

638
00:37:14,601 --> 00:37:15,600
This is amazing!

639
00:37:15,601 --> 00:37:17,600
Yes!

640
00:37:17,601 --> 00:37:22,600
Woohoo!

641
00:37:22,601 --> 00:37:24,600
Oh yeah!

642
00:37:24,601 --> 00:37:25,600
Human boomerang!

643
00:37:25,601 --> 00:37:26,600
He's actually flying.

644
00:37:26,601 --> 00:37:28,600
So are we.

645
00:37:28,601 --> 00:37:29,600
Whoa!

646
00:37:29,601 --> 00:37:30,600
That's my best friend!

647
00:37:30,601 --> 00:37:31,600
That's my best friend!

648
00:37:31,601 --> 00:37:32,600
Now you throw me!

649
00:37:32,601 --> 00:37:33,601
Now you throw me!

650
00:37:55,580 --> 00:38:03,580
I had no idea that you were going to die.

651
00:38:03,581 --> 00:38:05,980
This is only the beginning.

652
00:38:07,040 --> 00:38:15,040
I can't believe it.

653
00:38:16,240 --> 00:38:17,980
Airbenders will fill the sky again.

654
00:38:18,630 --> 00:38:20,420
We have been given a great gift.

655
00:38:21,420 --> 00:38:22,740
The chance to redeem ourselves.

656
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:26,040
You were destined to find
me on that mountain, Aang.

657
00:38:28,690 --> 00:38:29,700
How did you end up there?

658
00:38:34,410 --> 00:38:35,890
The Earthbenders had attacked Tirana.

659
00:38:37,210 --> 00:38:39,620
Sonim and I fought
fearlessly, side by side.

660
00:38:40,570 --> 00:38:41,930
We drove them back to Mount Baihu.

661
00:38:42,880 --> 00:38:44,120
And that's the last I remember.

662
00:38:46,740 --> 00:38:47,980
She must have saved your life.

663
00:38:48,880 --> 00:38:51,060
Only an Avatar could
have put you in that sphere.

664
00:38:55,060 --> 00:38:57,580
Aang, can I ask you something?

665
00:38:58,080 --> 00:38:59,080
Of course.

666
00:38:59,820 --> 00:39:02,977
If the Fire Nation destroyed
the Air Nomads, how

667
00:39:02,989 --> 00:39:05,960
can you suffer the
presence of the Fire Lord?

668
00:39:09,260 --> 00:39:10,840
Zuko is a friend and an ally.

669
00:39:11,840 --> 00:39:14,320
He turned against his own
father to help me end the war.

670
00:39:15,310 --> 00:39:17,480
Yet he wears the crown himself now.

671
00:39:18,630 --> 00:39:21,160
Fire by its nature burns, Aang.

672
00:39:22,310 --> 00:39:25,420
Our kind have always suffered at
the hands of the other elements.

673
00:39:27,270 --> 00:39:28,680
That's why we built Republic City.

674
00:39:29,780 --> 00:39:33,280
To show the world that if we listen
to each other, we can all live together.

675
00:39:33,281 --> 00:39:34,420
In peace.

676
00:39:36,250 --> 00:39:39,840
And once we bring back
Airbenders, it'll be complete.

677
00:39:43,790 --> 00:39:47,800
When everyone stuck to their own,
the whole world was nearly torn apart.

678
00:39:49,100 --> 00:39:54,700
And besides, Katara, Sokka,
Zuko, Toph, they're my family now.

679
00:39:56,480 --> 00:39:58,680
I want to live in a world
where we can all be together.

680
00:40:00,910 --> 00:40:02,820
You remind me so much of Sonom.

681
00:40:06,870 --> 00:40:08,680
It's the Avatar.

682
00:40:08,681 --> 00:40:11,440
And this time he's got
his friends with him.

683
00:40:11,890 --> 00:40:13,160
That's the Fire Lord's airship.

684
00:40:13,610 --> 00:40:14,560
How'd they get ahead of us?

685
00:40:14,561 --> 00:40:16,040
They don't even have the map.

686
00:40:16,290 --> 00:40:18,500
We can't risk him
getting to the staff first.

687
00:40:18,501 --> 00:40:19,380
Kill him.

688
00:40:19,381 --> 00:40:20,700
But he spared our lives.

689
00:40:20,701 --> 00:40:24,940
And how many Countless were killed in
the hundred years waiting for his return?

690
00:40:25,100 --> 00:40:27,720
